Rating: 4
Have made this several times and it has been very much enjoyed by everyone. I make this with my regular homemade pizza crust instead of the Boboli pre-made crusts --- it works just as well that way. First time I made it thought the raw garlic was a bit much --- but now I roast the garlic first and love the sweet roasted taste. If fresh tomatoes aren't in season, I've made this successfully with a chunky, basil tomato sauce -- different than with fresh tomatoes, but still quite good.

